transcript:
Customer: Hello
Executive: Hello
Customer: Haan ji.
Executive: Haan ji Rajendra ji, main actually CT baat kar rahi thi IndiaMART se, senior manager. To aapke TDS se related na hamare paas already concern aaya hua tha to main us cheez se related hi main aapse baat karna chah rahi thi ki jo TDS ka aap logon ne chalan vagaira bhara hoga na wo certificate aap mujhe ek baar de dijiye. Aapka ye same number WhatsApp pe rahega?
Customer: Main same number ye maine mail kiya hua hai wo fir bhi aapko WhatsApp kar dijiye main abhi aapko de deta hu same number WhatsApp mera.
Executive: Sorry sorry.
Customer: Maine aapko mail kiya hua hai jo customer wali customer care wali mail hoti hai usko mail kiya hua hai aur fir bhi aap mere ko WhatsApp kar dijiye main aapko WhatsApp kar deta hu abhi.
Executive: Haan main wahi bol rahi hu main aapko ek baar WhatsApp pe bhej rahi hu aap mujhe ek baar WhatsApp par bhi provide kara dijiye. Thik hai waise to aapka matlab mila hua hai hame mail but ek baar aap mujhe WhatsApp par provide kara dijiye main ye aapka refund kara deti hu. Thik hai.
Customer: Thik hai.
Executive: Aur baki matlab iske alawa aur to koi concern nahi hai na aap logon ko.
Customer: Nahi nahi aur koi concern aur koi concern nahi hai.
Executive: Thik hai thik hai to ye to main aapka kara deti hu sir baki ye jo aapka concern open hua tha fir main idhar side se close kar du na aap mere se directly fir us cheez thik hai aap mere se directly is cheez se related coordinate kar lijiyega main aapko apna personal number provide kara de rahi hu even calling number bhi WhatsApp number bhi thik hai. Koi bhi issue aata hai aap mere ko directly us cheez se related coordinate kar sakte ho aur ye wala main mail aapka close kar rahi hu matlab concern close kar rahi hu aap logon ke paas yaha pe jo bhi register mail id hai wo register mail id ka access hoga sir aapke paas?
Customer: Haan haan haan.
Executive: Thik hai to usse na mere feedback ke liye na aapke paas ek mail aayega ki aap satisfy hai ya nahi to waha pe bas aap positive feedback de dijiyega sir. Thik hai.
Customer: Thik hai.
Executive: Aur ye I think mail par bhi attach kiya hua hai aapne certificate apna.
Customer: Haan certificate aur bank detail bhi di hui hai.
Executive: Haan haan to wo mujhe mil gaya hai koi issue nahi hai thik hai to aap nahi bhi bhejenge to chalega ye mujhe mil gaya hai yaha pe main karwati hu sir aapka ye process thik hai.
Customer: Okay okay okay.
Executive: Okay okay thank you.
